room_title: Escape room "Cell Block D - Dystopia" by iEscape Rooms in Wilmington
room_address: 100 N Lake Park Blvd, Carolina Beach NC 28428
room_description: There is an old prison just outside of town that has been placed under federal investigation stemming from some disturbing rumors and stories that inmates keep going missing. You and your team have been recruited by the FBI to go in undercover and try to unravel these rumors and stories. Beware, the last agent that went in... hasn't made it out!
